death sentence has been approved by the higher authorities. We should not insult them, take away their personal 
effects or try to exact taxation from them, but without exception should treat them sincerely and kindly.

  		-- Mao Zedong, "Quotations From Chairman Mao", XII. Political Work (1940)
%
The contest of strength is not only a contest of military and economic power, but also a contest of human power and morale.

  		-- Mao Zedong, "Quotations From Chairman Mao", XII. Political Work (1958)
%
Ideological education is the key link to be grasped in uniting the whole Party for great political struggles. 
