  		-- Mao Zedong, "Quotations From Chairman Mao", XIII. Relations Between Officers and Men (1957)
%
The army must become one with the people so that they see it as their own army. Such an army will be invincible.

  		-- Mao Zedong, "Quotations From Chairman Mao", XIV. Relations Between the Army and the People (1938)
