We should be modest and prudent, guard against arrogance and rashness, and serve the Chinese people heart and soul.

  		-- Mao Zedong, "Quotations From Chairman Mao", XVII. Serving the People (1945)
%
Comrade Norman Bethune's spirit, his utter devotion to others without any thought of self, was shown in his 
